                            <h2>CloudForms Management Engine (CFME) - ManageIQ (Community Version)</h2>
                            <hr class="star-primary">
                            <img src="img/portfolio/manageIQ.png" class="img-responsive img-centered" alt="" style="width:160px;height:160px;">
                    		<ul class="list-inline item-details">
                                <li>Date:
                                    <strong><a href=#>Mach 2013 - Till Date</a>
                                    </strong>
                                </li>
                                <li>Role:
                                    <strong><a href=#>Sr. Quality Engineer</a>
                                    </strong>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
			<p align="justify">The EVM Suite enables organizations to deploy, manage and optimize private, public and hybrid clouds,
virtualized infrastructures and virtual desktops. Built on <a href="http://manageiq.org/">ManageIQ’s</a> patent-pending Adaptive Management PlatformTM, EVM delivers unified monitoring, management and automation through a single pane of glass across enterprise clouds and globally distributed datacenters.</p>
			<img src="img/portfolio/manageiq2.jpg" class="img-responsive img-centered" alt="">
			<button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal"><i class="fa fa-times"></i> Close</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
